description:
Stack Dash is new free fun game, Swipe the stack dash cube collectin to keep going forward and step further in the levels.
stack the stacky dash cube and make a really tall stack tower to dash the player forward to the finish line to get win the sacky maze level.
A fun stack and dash game with a satisfying level way and It's suitable for all gamers stack and dash game tower.
A really great time killer for many hours gameplay with tile stacky dash to think for stack and collect most of the cubes in stacky dash game.
Move the stack to the right cube color in the maze and finally get a huge score boost in a satisfying way!
Remember that stacking cube helps you grow your tower stack dash and you will need to find the right path to dash and stack all the cubes to surfing to the next maze
Stack Dash Game Features
◉ Simple & Beautiful graphics designed
◉ Compete for the best Opponents
◉ satisfying Stack Short maze Challenges
◉ Fun stacky mazes and gameplay
◉ Great Time Killer for hours gameplay
◉ New free stack game with Satisfying way
you don"t need a guide, Just stack and dash and enjoy!
